ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectKingdom of the Netherlands - Exchange of Notes constituting an Amendment to the Agreement on Mutual Administrative Assistance in Customs Matters (Ratification)
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to bring into force, for Canada, the EXCHANGE OF NOTES constituting an AMENDMENT to the AGREEMENT between the Government of Canada and the Government of the Kingdom of the NETHERLANDS on Mutual Administrative Assistance in Customs Matters.
